'''Corellian Transport Services''' was a small, local business on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]], transporting both civilians and cargo across the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] and [[Mirax Terrik Horn]] used one of their [[Air taxi/Legends|hovertaxis]] to escape a [[Voxyn]] in [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]].

